Benefits and Services






Benefits and Services



Please check with all programs, clinics and services for any changes to procedures due to COVID-19.
As UIC alumni, you have access to a variety of exclusive benefits, which you can begin taking advantage of immediately upon graduation. These benefits* include:

Access to health care, libraries and fitness facilities
Discounted family-friendly services and facilities
Resources to support business and leadership development
Unique experiences such as UIC sporting events, Jane Addams Hull-House Museum and live theatre
Opportunities to pursue continuing education courses and certificate programs

We invite you to explore these extensive resources and hope you enjoy being UIC alumni!
*Benefits are updated annually and may vary; always contact host office directly for hours and offerings prior to event or program.





